## Coordination Protocol

Agents:
- Glance at `TASKS.md` every ~30 min for changes.
- Check `git log --oneline -10` every ~15-30 min to see others' work.
- Update this file + commit after finishing a unit.

Team lead:
- Review progress every ~30 min; run `git log`.
- Resolve blockers/conflicts; keep `TASKS.md` current.
